event.description: Ramón Laureano singles to shallow right field. Seth Brown to third.
Yandy Díaz doubles to deep left field.
Josh VanMeter flies out to deep center field to Victor Robles.
Yordan Alvarez pops out to shallow infield to Luis Guillorme.
Wander Franco pops out to second base to Luis Urías.
Brandon Nimmo doubles to left center field.
César Hernández singles to left field.
Stephen Piscotty doubles to left field. Ramón Laureano scores. Seth Brown scores.
Starling Marte flies out to center field to Jake Meyers.
